definitions.definition: Any of several plant-eating mammals of the genus Lepus , similar to a rabbit , but larger and with longer ears.
The player in a paperchase , or hare and hounds game, who leaves a trail of paper to be followed.

main_definition: ( countable ) Any of several plant-eating mammals of the genus Lepus , similar to a rabbit , but larger and with longer ears.
secondary_definitions: ( uncountable ) The meat from this animal.
( countable ) The player in a paperchase , or hare and hounds game, who leaves a trail of paper to be followed.
